        <h2 class="c-linz-dark-purple">You might be able to find what you're looking for through one of these links:</h2> 
<p class="linzess-not-found-links c-linz-dark-purple"><a href="/understanding-constipation#typesofconstipation" data-digitaldata="{&quot;digitalData&quot;:{&quot;page&quot;:{&quot;link&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Learn more about the types of constipation&quot;,&quot;displayTitle&quot;:&quot;Learn more about the types of constipation&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;internal&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;/understanding-constipation/types-of-constipation&quot;},&quot;component&quot;:{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;content&quot;,&quot;l10title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;system error&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;RTE&quot;,&quot;position&quot;:&quot;content&quot;},&quot;interaction&quot;:{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;rte-1522840544-0&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Learn more about the types of constipation&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;content&quot;},&quot;mva&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;tier&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;&quot;}}}}">Learn more about the types of constipation</a></p> 
<p class="linzess-not-found-links"><a href="/why-linzess#howlinzessworks" data-digitaldata="{&quot;digitalData&quot;:{&quot;page&quot;:{&quot;link&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Find out how LINZESS works&quot;,&quot;displayTitle&quot;:&quot;Find out how LINZESS works&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;internal&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;/why-linzess/how-linzess-works&quot;},&quot;component&quot;:{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;content&quot;,&quot;l10title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;system error&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;RTE&quot;,&quot;position&quot;:&quot;content&quot;},&quot;interaction&quot;:{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;rte-1522840544-1&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Find out how LINZESS works&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;content&quot;},&quot;mva&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;tier&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;&quot;}}}}">Find out how LINZESS works</a></p> 
<p class="linzess-not-found-links"><a href="/find-relief/gutcheck" data-digitaldata="{&quot;digitalData&quot;:{&quot;page&quot;:{&quot;link&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Take the 5-question Gut Check&quot;,&quot;displayTitle&quot;:&quot;Take the 5-question Gut Check&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;internal&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;/find-relief/gutcheck&quot;},&quot;component&quot;:{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;content&quot;,&quot;l10title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;system error&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;RTE&quot;,&quot;position&quot;:&quot;content&quot;},&quot;interaction&quot;:{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;rte-1522840544-2&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Take the 5-question Gut Check&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;content&quot;},&quot;mva&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;tier&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;&quot;}}}}">Take the 5-question Gut Check</a></p>
